Class CommandVisitor.Adapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.internal.recordstorage.CommandVisitor.Adapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CommandVisitor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TransactionApplier.Adapter
    Enclosing interface:
    CommandVisitor
    public static class CommandVisitor.Adapter
extends Object
implements CommandVisitor
    An empty implementation of a CommandVisitor. Allows you to implement only the methods you are interested in. See also TransactionApplier.Adapter if need handle commands inside of a transaction, or have a lock.
